        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱兩萬七未穩 恒指升268點報26877點 阿里孖寶領漲 登場新股升幅收窄",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早全程報升，可惜未能企穩於兩萬七點之上為半日市作結。阿里孖寶齊漲逾3%，登場新股亦全部造好，但較招股價升幅均見收窄。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250901_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250901_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數甫開市即有挑戰兩萬七之勢，開升350點、報26958點，未幾已升越27000點，中段最高曾衝上27143點，將升幅擴大至535點，其後便進入由高位拾級回吐的階段，於大約10時半過後失守27000點，最低報26839點，升幅縮至230點，早市尾段仍反覆試底。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250901_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250901_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250901_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指中午以26877點收市，升268點或1.01%。恒生科技指數跑輸大市，半日升22點或0.38%，報5885點；國企指數升73點或0.8%，報9293點。主板半日成交1920.31億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升312點，報26909點，高水32點。科指期貨升38點，報5901點，高水16點。國指期貨升94點，報9306點，高水12點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)ADR昨晚折合每股收升逾5%，該股今早在港表現自然備受注意，而阿里系兩隻藍籌亦未令投資者失望，早市雙雙躋身藍籌升幅10大榜上。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴再創1個月高位，最高曾見164元，漲6.29%，低位159元時也升3.05%；中午收報159.7元，升3.5%，單一股份已為恒指提供近72點進賬。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同系阿里健康(00241)延續昨天升勢，今早衝上3個月高位，最高報6.79元，升6.76%；中午收報6.57元，仍漲3.3%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241128_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其餘重磅科股則個別發展，在「ATMXJ」當中三升兩跌，除了阿里巴巴揚升外，騰訊(00700)微升0.48%，報626元；京東(09618)升1.11%，報118.2元。美團(03690)則回吐0.86%，報104.1元；近期相對弱勢的小米(01810)，今早也跌0.67%，報38.48元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天強勢的快手(01024)與百度(09888)，今早同樣回落。快手跌1.93%，報78.7元；百度跌1.38%，報142.7元。網易(09999)則升0.45%，報224.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早藍籌升幅榜前列，改由藥股佔領。藥明康德(02359)昨天收市後發盈喜，料2025年盈利增長逾倍，該股今早應聲漲7.85%，報119.5元；同系藥明生物(02269)也升4.31%，報39.2元，兩股分別成為藍籌升幅榜的冠軍及季軍。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明康德官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250403_FI_source-web_02359-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明康德官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">表現次佳藍籌落在石藥集團(01093)身上，中午收報10元，升5.71%；翰森製藥(03692)升3.89%，報42.22元；中國生物製藥(01177)則漲3.8%，報7.11元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金融股亦是升市主要功臣，當中以兩隻藍籌內險股升勢最突出，中國人壽(02628)再創逾10年高位，中午收報32.72元，升2.64%；中國平安(02318)升2.04%，報69.9元。兩大藍籌國際金融股造好，滙控(00005)升1.85%，報126.4元；友邦(01299)升0.96%，報84.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">部份二線生物製藥股亦炒上，榮昌生物(09995)與艾伯維簽署授權許可，該股今早應聲飆 %，報 元；康龍化成(03759)升 %，報 元；雲頂新耀(01952)升 %，報 元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地車企同樣受捧，歐盟宣布與中國就電動車輸入歐盟的關稅問題達成共識。歐盟為此發布指導意見，要求中國電動車出口商提交價格承諾書。意味中國電動車進入歐盟市場，必須提出最低價格。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪(01211)升3.19%，報98.75元；吉利汽車(00175)升1.18%，報17.12元；理想汽車(02015)也升1.15%，報65.8元。小鵬汽車(09868)創1個月高位，報82.8元，升3.05%；零跑汽車(09863)升2.44%，報48.66元；蔚來(09866)升1.33%，報38.06元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價再揚，不少金礦股今早破頂創新高，其中紫金礦業(02889)升2.8%，報40.38元；同系紫金黃金(02259)升5.56%，報161.5元；招金礦業(01818)升1.59%，報37.12元；靈寶黃金(03330)升5.38%，報21.56元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/紫金礦業官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">碳酸鋰期貨主力合約日內漲11.99%，觸及漲停，也是連續第二天漲停，兩隻鋰業股借勢炒上。贛鋒鋰業(01772)升4.82%，報62元；天齊鋰業(09696)升2.91%，報56.65元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日共有3隻新股掛牌，早市全程企於招股價之上，只是中午較招股價升幅均已收窄。在GEM上市的BBSB(08610)今早以3元開市，較招股價0.6元高4倍；中午收報0.99元，僅高於招股價65%。在兩隻主板掛牌新股中，紅星冷鏈(01641)中午收報12.8，較招股價12.26元僅高4.41%；兆易創新(03986)中午收報226.8元，較招股價162元高40%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15578206-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83%e6%9c%aa%e7%a9%a9-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87268%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126877%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%ad%96%e5%af%b6%e9%a0%98",
