        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市反覆爭持 生物製藥板塊再現強勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市今早呈反覆爭持局面，滬深兩市半日交投已達2.435萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。生物製藥板塊資金流入明顯，榮昌生物(09995)A股(688331.SH)飆20%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"榮昌生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/09995-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"榮昌生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/09995-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">榮昌生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早高開4點後進入好淡爭持格局，早段最多曾倒跌24點，低見4141點，未幾迅速轉升，最高報4179點，升14點，早市全程大部份時間在升或跌10點之間波動；滬指中午收報4163點，跌1點或0.03%，半日成交9667.76億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指相對反覆偏軟，最高報14458點，升91點，低位14251點時則跌115點，於上午10時15分過後便一直報跌；深指中午收報14321點，跌45點或0.31%，成交1.47萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數則升不足1點或0.01%，收報4790點；創業板指數跌28點或0.83%，報3360點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在各主要板塊中，以生物製藥資金流入情況最明顯。榮昌生物A股是A+H成員中表現最佳的A股，中午收市前漲20%封板，報114.46元；藥明康德(02359)A股(603259.SH)升5.76%，報104.36元；康龍化成(03759)A股(300759.SZ)升5.55%，報33.3元；泰格醫藥(03347)A股(300347.SZ)升4.95%，報62.74元；昭衍新藥(06127)A股(603127.SH)也升4.06%，報42.02元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15578071-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e8%a3%bd%e8%97%a5%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e5%86%8d%e7%8f%be%e5%bc%b7%e5%8b%a2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-1-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 11:45:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股早市中段升幅逐漸收窄 兩萬七得復失暫升不足300點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早一度重越兩萬七關口，但恒生指數衝上27143點、升534點後暫欠再升動力，於上午約10時半過後重新回吐至27000點之下。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約11時04分，恒生指數升幅收窄至293點或1.1%，報26902點；恒生科技指數升0.71%，恒生金融分類指數則升1.17%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升幅收窄至約3.4%，滙控(00005)與友邦(01299)升幅亦縮至不足2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15577971-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e9%80%90%e6%bc%b8%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83%e5%be%97%e5%be%a9%e5%a4%b1%e6%9a%ab%e5%8d%87%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b33",
